jbiclustge.methods.algorithms.java.bicat.auxtools

Class Option

  • java.lang.Object
    • jbiclustge.methods.algorithms.java.bicat.auxtools.Option

  • public class Option
extends Object
    This class contains option flags which have to be set at compile time. The option flags were introduced to keep the command line parameter list short while making programmers life easier, as message level and other options can be changed without editing much program code.
    Version:
    2004-07-22
    Author:
    Thomas Frech
